        public Koohii.DiffCalc calc(int mods,
                            double singletap_threshold)
        calculates beatmap difficulty and stores it in total, aim, speed, nsingles, nsingles_speed fields.
        Parameters:
        singletap_threshold - the smallest milliseconds interval that will be considered singletappable. for example, 125ms is 240 1/2 singletaps ((60000 / 240) / 2)

        self
